  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Ramadan Fasting has multiple effects on the variation of hematological and biochemical
      parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective observational study, including patients with cardiovascular risk
      factors and doing the fast of Ramadan with assessment before, during and after the month of
      Ramadan.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
